        </mj-text>

        <mj-text font-size="16px" color="#000000" font-family="Roboto Mono">
          <sup>*</sup>LNURL supporting Lightning wallets:<br />
          BLW, Blixt, BlueWallet, Breez, coinos, LNbits, @lntxbot, Phoenix, Shockwallet, ThunderHub, Wallet of Satoshi, Zap-Android, Zap-iOS, ZEBEDEE, Zeus
        </mj-text>

        <mj-text font-size="16px" font-family="Roboto Mono">
          Open a Lightning channel with us:
        </mj-text>

        <mj-text font-size="16px" font-family="Roboto Mono">
          028f4a60dd133875e8776d5ac36e87097cf59e6e3a1d74fcd14c900270dda57c06@54.211.84.101:9735
        </mj-text>

        <mj-text font-size="16px" font-family="Roboto Mono">
          028f4a60dd133875e8776d5ac36e87097cf59e6e3a1d74fcd14c900270dda57c06@5whetw27qqbdm626znqc75evlfasljfamecssktqfz3vrnl3qpkqpnyd.onion:9735
        </mj-text>

        <mj-text font-size="16px" color="#000000" font-family="Roboto Mono">Happy Bidding, <br />
          <mj-raw>
            <a href="https://scarce.city">
              Scarce City</a>
          </mj-raw>
        </mj-text>

        <mj-text color="#000000" font-family="Roboto Mono">
          <a href=%unsubscribe_url%>Unsubscribe<a>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
  </mj-body>
</mjml>
